flowchart TD
    A[Wave Candidate] --> B{Smoke Test Exists?}
    B -- No --> X[Block Wave]
    B -- Yes --> C{Architecture Boundary Test Exists?}
    C -- No --> Y[Ready With Note]
    C -- Yes --> D{Forbidden Collapse Protected?}
    D -- No --> X
    D -- Yes --> E{Dependencies From Earlier Waves Only?}
    E -- No --> X
    E -- Yes --> F[Wave May Proceed]
    F --> G[Compile]
    G --> H{Pass?}
    H -- No --> X
    H -- Yes --> I[Wave Accepted As Skeleton]
